---
// CustomerSegments.astro
---
<section class="section" id="customers">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-label">🏦 Who It's For</div>
      <h2>Built for regulated organizations deploying agentic AI.</h2>
      <p>Phronesis is designed for institutions operating under regulatory scrutiny where AI systems must be explainable, auditable, and production-ready.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="segments-grid">
      <!-- Segment 1: Beachhead -->
      <div class="segment-card card segment--primary" id="segment-banks">
        <div class="segment-badge">
          <span class="badge badge-cyan">⭐ Primary Market</span>
        </div>
        <div class="segment-header">
          <div class="segment-icon">🏦</div>
          <div>
            <h3>Regional & Mid-Market Banks</h3>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="segment-why" style="margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 1rem;">Deploying agentic AI under DORA, SR 26-2, and evolving AI governance requirements - without the internal infrastructure needed to reconstruct AI incidents at scale.</p>
        <p class="segment-why" style="margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 1rem;">Phronesis provides the forensic visibility needed to safely operationalize AI systems.</p>


      </div>

      <!-- Segment 2: FinTechs -->
      <div class="segment-card card segment--secondary" id="segment-fintechs">
        <div class="segment-badge">
          <span class="badge badge-blue">⭐ Secondary Market</span>
        </div>
        <div class="segment-header">
          <div class="segment-icon">🚀</div>
          <div>
            <h3>Regulated FinTechs</h3>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="segment-why" style="margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 1rem;">Scaling AI-driven financial products while maintaining auditability, incident traceability, and governance readiness across rapidly evolving systems.</p>
        <p class="segment-why" style="margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 1rem;">Phronesis helps modern AI infrastructure remain explainable under regulatory scrutiny.</p>


  </div>
</section>

<style>
.segments-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 1fr;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.segment-card {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1rem;
}

.segment--primary {
  border-color: rgba(0,212,255,0.2);
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-surface) 0%, rgba(0,212,255,0.02) 100%);
}

.segment-badge {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 0.5rem;
}
.segment-years {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.68rem;
  color: var(--color-text-dim);
}

.segment-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 0.75rem;
}
.segment-icon { font-size: 2rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
.segment-header h3 { font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.1rem; }
.segment-sub { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--color-text-dim); font-family: var(--font-mono); }

.segment-jurisdictions { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.4rem; }

.segment-why { font-size: 0.9rem; }
.segment-why strong { color: var(--color-cyan); }

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .segments-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
</style>
